WEBVTT

00:11.778 --> 00:14.648
The timber wolves are a-howlin'!

00:14.998 --> 00:17.694
The timber wolves are a-howlin'!

00:20.541 --> 00:21.544
Eyup.

00:22.005 --> 00:23.323
The Zap Apples are comin'!

00:23.573 --> 00:25.300
The Zap Apples are comin'!

00:26.130 --> 00:26.889
Yay!

00:27.239 --> 00:28.794
The Zap Apples are comin'!

00:29.431 --> 00:30.777
That's what I said.

